Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼請您在回收同意書上籤名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要和米拉貝爾離別什麼的 會變的寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這孩子是小熊小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼關於米拉貝爾的回收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持有者的您有三個方案可選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一是 重新購買的折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二是 舊換新來得到定價的三成現金回饋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三是 植入新的OS在米拉貝爾的身體中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說 換上新的人格繼續使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煩請您植入新的OS了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個… 人格和記憶都會消失喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 以前就是這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前就是 是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:01:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使更換了靈魂我也依然把她當作同一個人對待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更換了OS之後的吉芙提爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有沒有可能在某種情況下恢復了以前的記憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有呢 從來沒有先例
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到處亂晃就是為了問這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才受不了外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉 滿還是一如既往的咄咄逼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提爾的這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和人類喪失記憶是完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}內在被完全替換成全新的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經是不同的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完完全全的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這點上可不要搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就可以認為無可奈何而果斷接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓人空有期望白白等待才更痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我也能夠理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在來這裡之前也曾經想過相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以必須想辦法讓自己去接受這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這也是沒有辦法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天第三終端服務派遣的執行者會到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們負責的所有者和回收對象聽說躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有情報說他們潛伏在我們的負責區域內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就派人來搜索了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然提出這個要求是在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是希望你們可以去支援她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們就是司和艾拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是第三終端服務的安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說回來 安迪的搭檔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出差要執行者一個人去才是基本政策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一終端服務不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒出差過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特地派兩個人出來效率很低不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在出差地會準備像你們這樣的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不會有什麼困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果艾拉去出差的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我肯定也會跟去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出差什麼的我一個人也是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 沒有聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個真是奇怪的組合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奧利維拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的知心好友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在摸哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒想到你居然會反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明以前不管摸多久都不會反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過這樣也有這樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說…兩位是認識的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們可是一同度過了青春時代的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們不是第一次見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉你跟我朋友長得太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不小心認錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還真是冒失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一終端服務這邊的人都好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們能就此放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請在這裡簽字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託 放過他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想離開德瑞克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我愛他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那至少到期限為止讓我和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一週左右的話沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們又會逃跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}德瑞克！ 德瑞克！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}托你們的福 回收的進程比計劃快了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？ 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有必要那麼強硬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣的話 和持有者引發矛盾也不足為奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}銷毀回憶是我們的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪並沒有錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒不如說終端服務一般都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有我們不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還要照顧持有者和回收對象的心理感受什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再說這還是香月三年前開始使用的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就因為這個課長還經常被總部叫過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為經費花得太多被發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道你在等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我剛才去找康孝先生請教了一下關於今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想參與你請教的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 那下次就和艾拉聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的長得一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 今天就這樣 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才是安迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前的事想道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就打電話給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後就完全被喜歡上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受歡迎的女性真不好過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 聽你們對話好像你之前就認識安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們以前是鄰居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她當時叫奧莉維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當時？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這真的是安迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺給人印象不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奧莉維亞在幾年前被回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是…更換了OS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看啊 終端服務不是總說要削減經費嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以本來應該被銷毀的奧莉維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就被重新利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪還有身為奧莉維亞那時候的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒想到還能以這種形式再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然還能揉到那胸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奧莉維亞的 雖然現在是安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前可是經常讓我揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正確的說是我強行去揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這人已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那已經不是奧莉維亞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐已經不在意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種事不值得在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概是這樣的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}點心送到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 誰送的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三終端服務的課長送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 沏茶麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幾天前來的安迪幹活真是俐落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給人一種「刷刷」地搞定工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「嗖」地就回來了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗚哇 這是在說我們不中用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 並不是那個意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不小心和安迪說了我老家嘉年華的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後她非要我帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但那個嘉年華是今晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以司司 拜託和我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個人好好玩一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為那裡全是和奧莉維亞在一起的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和安迪一起去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太折磨人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟長得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司～ 跟我一起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就當作幫我一個忙 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}呃 不 等等 啊啊 別抱這麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個人在偷偷摸摸幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真的很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連搭檔都不告訴肯定有問題不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒有特別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很在意對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…只是舉例而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帶安迪去嘉年華的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以此為契機奧莉維亞的記憶可能會回來一些些… 有可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在思考著艾拉拉的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無論我說什麼你都不會那麼簡單就認同的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說沒關係 司司就盡情的利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}利用是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚一起去吧 然後在那邊用自己的雙眼去確認就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用勉強也沒關係喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是司的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順帶一提 安迪也會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 繪瑠小姐也會跟著去唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 那就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最後還會放煙火 很熱鬧的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我從來都沒實際看過煙火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒看過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聲音很大 你一定會嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把耳朵塞起來比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 不 不用塞起來也沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 所以說沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿 還真多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉超可愛 超可愛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總感覺好興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很少有機會來這種地方呢 成為繪瑠的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就到處逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司… 司！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都只有我和繪瑠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也應該幫艾拉照幾張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪 我們喝點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊 有些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 要看嗎 就像好姐妹一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 要不艾拉也來照一張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 沒有聽清楚 請再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個…拍張照…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拍照…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您 您心情不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個 來看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水母果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姑且也算是這個嘉年華的名產果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無法想像什麼味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼嘛 喝喝看不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 安迪還是別喝比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯～ 真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然是第一次喝 但味道還不賴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 是嗎 還不賴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯～ 繪瑠不敢喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛…嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 那個… 那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來吧 艾拉也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小心點別走散囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我… 又不是小孩子了 才不會走散…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 這個你也來喝喝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…但是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走散了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惡 大叔再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪好像很快樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}逛了不少地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼樣 你覺得她的記憶有恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 這就是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明年肯定不會再來這嘉年華了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為替代 我會和安迪一起去別的地方玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想安迪和奧利維亞共享記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是希望創造出新的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不這樣的話 無論是對安迪還是奧利維亞都很失敬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你今天陪我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多虧了你 我感覺甩掉了包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不甩掉…不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 小司 能創造回憶的只有當下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能在這當下這須臾間去創造
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當下這須臾間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 艾拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 難道是走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作起來啊 男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 讓你一個人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聲音真的很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪的記憶沒有恢復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是不是讓司很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你能夠說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想讓司因為和我搭檔而承受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胸膛都要裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想要一直做艾拉的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼要堅持到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還問為什麼 那種事肯定是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為 我喜歡艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為 我喜歡艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說出口了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為 為什麼啊！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
